<p>Zimpu ritual incense and its special manner of preparation is one of the ancient traditional arts of the monastic order of Tibet. Snowlion incense is composed of 55 ingredients of which saffron, nagi, red and white sandalwood form part. A lovely fresh and clean burning incense. Each pack of Snowlion contains 65 gram of incense (approx 44 sticks) and the sticks are approx 17cm long.</p>